<div class='m1 module'>
<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>Women</h1>
<div class='p1'>
A collection of TED Talks (and more) on the topic of women.
</div>
</div>
<div class='row'>
<div class='col col-lg-sidebarred'>
<div class='section section--minor'>
<!--[if lte IE 8]>
<style>
@import url("https://tedcdnpa-a.akamaihd.net/stylesheets/pages/dynamic/topics-ie.css?1449612282");
</style>
<![endif]-->
<!--[if gt IE 8]><!-->
<style scoped>
@import url("https://tedcdnpa-a.akamaihd.net/stylesheets/pages/dynamic/topics.css?1449612282");
</style>
<!--<![endif]-->
<h3 class="h4 m3">Video playlists about Women</h3>
<div class='row row-skinny row-sm-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Barbra Streisand: 8 must-see talks for women</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/48/barbra_streisand_8_must_see_t'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/barbra_streisand_playlists.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
8 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 05m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>An advocate for women's health, Barbra Streisand founded the Barbra Streisand Women’s Heart Center -- whose director is TEDxWomen star Dr. C. Noel Bairey Merz. Together they pick some great talks for women and, really, anyone.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>10 talks by women that everyone should watch</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/192/10_talks_by_women_that_everyon'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/10_talks_by_women.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 38m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Color bravery. A headset for brainwaves. His/hers healthcare. 10 big, bold talks from female speakers. </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>The importance of educating girls</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/193/the_importance_of_educating_gi'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/education_for_girls.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
5 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 13m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>In far too many countries around the world, an education is not a given for girls. These moving talks are from those facing great risk to change that.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Talks to make you feel good about getting older</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/227/talks_to_make_you_feel_good_ab'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/getting_older.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
6 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 07m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>The extra candles on the birthday cake, the little lines you notice in the mirror ... aging doesn’t always feel good. But remember, age also brings wisdom and balance. Watch these reminders of the benefits that come with age. </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
